&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The&amp;nbsp;venue…&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;SOHO HOUSE BERLIN is a private members&#39; club and hotel in a listed building in the heart of the capital. In addition to restaurants, a fitness studio, rooftop pool, in-house cinema and a spacious spa area, the hotel offers 65 rooms in various sizes, 20 flats and four lofts. In addition to Berlin and Great Britain, there are other houses in the USA, Toronto, Barcelona, Amsterdam, Istanbul and Mumbai. The SOHO HOUSE includes the concept store THE STORE X. THE STORE X is a platform for ideas and culture. The range includes fashion, art, design and also attracts a global community of creative people to 180 The Strand in London, Soho House Berlin and Soho Farmhouse in Oxfordshire. Our aim is to present a new kind of experience space that exceeds customer expectations of traditional retail and shopping.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong data-redactor-tag=&quot;strong&quot;&gt;The role...&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The &lt;strong data-start=&quot;36&quot; data-end=&quot;50&quot;&gt;Accountant&lt;/strong&gt; is responsible for supporting the financial operations of the hotel and members’ club by maintaining accurate financial records, processing transactions, and assisting with financial reporting, reconciliations, and budget monitoring. The role ensures that all accounting activities are carried out accurately and in compliance with internal procedures and financial regulations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Accountabilities...&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;64&quot; data-end=&quot;163&quot;&gt;Preparation of weekly, monthly, and annual reports, including the related account reconciliations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;167&quot; data-end=&quot;243&quot;&gt;Supporting the tax office with VAT returns and annual financial statements&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;247&quot; data-end=&quot;301&quot;&gt;Managing the general ledger and fixed asset register&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;305&quot; data-end=&quot;376&quot;&gt;Handling accounts receivable, including issuing customer invoices&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;380&quot; data-end=&quot;445&quot;&gt;Handling accounts payable, including preparing payment runs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;449&quot; data-end=&quot;525&quot;&gt;Entering and reconciling delivery notes in the inventory management system&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;529&quot; data-end=&quot;595&quot;&gt;Monitoring payments and managing the dunning/collections process&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;599&quot; data-end=&quot;635&quot;&gt;Handling daily cash reconciliation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;639&quot; data-end=&quot;682&quot;&gt;Posting and reconciling bank transactions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;687&quot; data-end=&quot;732&quot;&gt;Maintaining vendor and customer master data&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;737&quot; data-end=&quot;805&quot;&gt;Preparing statistical reports (e.g., intra-community acquisitions)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;810&quot; data-end=&quot;917&quot;&gt;Acting as a contact person for internal and external inquiries related to accounts payable and receivable&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;922&quot; data-end=&quot;978&quot;&gt;Leading, supporting, and working closely with the team&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Experience Required...&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1004&quot; data-end=&quot;1046&quot;&gt;Independent and meticulous working style&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1050&quot; data-end=&quot;1109&quot;&gt;Fluent in German and English, both written and spoken&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1113&quot; data-end=&quot;1155&quot;&gt;Strong affinity for working with numbers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1159&quot; data-end=&quot;1200&quot;&gt;High level of commitment and initiative&lt;/li&gt;
