&lt;h2&gt;Key Responsibilities – Assistant Waiter&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As an Assistant Waiter, you play an important role in creating memorable dining experiences for our members and guests. Working alongside the service team, you&#39;ll ensure every interaction reflects Soho House&#39;s commitment to genuine hospitality, attention to detail and exceptional service.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Guest Experience&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Deliver warm, engaging and personalised service, ensuring every member and guest feels welcomed and valued.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Support the team in achieving guest satisfaction and departmental service goals while contributing to food and beverage revenue targets.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Follow Soho House service standards and sequence of service across breakfast, lunch, dinner, private events and special occasions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Engage with guests throughout their dining experience, anticipating their needs and responding promptly to feedback or requests.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Resolve minor service concerns confidently and escalate any operational issues to the Club Manager or Supervisor where appropriate.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Service Operations&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Assist in preparing, setting and maintaining restaurant sections to the highest standards before, during and after service.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Escort members and guests, reset tables efficiently and provide seamless support to ensure smooth restaurant operations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Complete daily opening, closing and side duties as allocated by the Head of Department or Supervisor.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Communicate special requests, guest preferences and operational updates promptly to the management team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Maintain exceptional knowledge of menus, daily specials and service procedures.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Standards &amp;amp; Compliance&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Consistently uphold Soho House brand standards, ensuring attention to detail in every aspect of service.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Maintain impeccable personal grooming and professional appearance in line with company guidelines.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Follow all food safety, hygiene, health and safety policies and operational procedures.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Attend all scheduled training sessions and actively participate in learning and development opportunities.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Comply with all company policies, procedures and code of conduct while promoting a positive and collaborative team culture.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Assistant Waiter&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;The Role…&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;We are seeking a skilled and passionate Assistant Waiter to join the team. You’ll have at least 2 years of experience in busy, high profile venues and a natural flair for first class service. You’ll be reliable, friendly and happy to be a key part of the team that strives for success.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;As part of our Soho House team your role is to make sure that our members have an amazing experience every time. Possessing natural hospitality charm, we will give you a platform to connect, grow, have fun and make an impact.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Assistant Waiter &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Benefits &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Soho Roc House offers a competitive salary with career development opportunities, based on the candidate&#39;s qualifications and skills. By joining our team, you will have the opportunity to work in a stimulating and motivating environment which values and is committed towards its employees.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;When you join you will receive a load of amazing benefits, including:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Meal provided whilst on shift&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Discount on all Cowshed products&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cookhouse &amp;amp; House Tonic: Our Cookhouse &amp;amp; House Tonic programmes offer unique food and drink trainings, events and opportunities to inspire and educate.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;We’ll support you with the tools and training you need to develop yourself personally and professionally&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Soho Roc House offers a seasonal working contract from May to October.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What we are looking for – Assistant Waiter&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Team player who communicates well with all colleagues&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Punctual, reliable and trustworthy&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Sense of urgency&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Yes, yes, yes mentality&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Can do attitude&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Have a genuine passion for food and beverage&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Previous experience within hospitality or service-based industry would be ideal but not essential&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to work with little supervision and maintain a high level of performance&lt;/li&gt;
